dict.string: Please come join our last meeting of the semster, where a fecing competition will be held between John Kim from USC, and Tim Frank from UCLA. Come support your player and school ! Pizza and beverage will be provided to the first 100 guests.

7550 E Spring St, Long Beach, CA 90808
